{
  "stem": "22840.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had a 1,000-page document that he has written without any paragraph, almost without any periods, not divided into anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was 1,000 page paragraph.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a memoir.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- I-- I classify it as a cry of wounded animal.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I undertook to put it in a computer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it's recorded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And eventually, it was published.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I excerpted from that a little part relating to his meeting with my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He essentially heard-- he was in Banska Bystrica.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Eventually came with all the people who came and joined the fighting group in Banska Bystrica.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And he was a-- he was a Polish Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And eventually, he heard about my mother because my father was quite well-known around the jury.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he heard that my mother was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow they established contact And talked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When it was clear that Banska Bystrica is going to fall to the Germans, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the party's own forces were retreating.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother pleaded with him to take her and her two children with them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he refused because he said they're going to the mountain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's no place for a woman and two little children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In 1944, I was seven years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was October.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was just turned seven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My sister was four years younger, three-- three or four years younger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Eventually, she prevailed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Eventually, she prevailed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he took her and myself and my sister with her-- with the whole partisan group, with a whole slew of refugees.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I identified on the map all the areas that we were because three years ago I went back to Slovakia eventually.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
